    public enum JCoFunctionUnitState
extends Enum<JCoFunctionUnitState>
    Defines possible function unit states.

    • Enum Constant Summary

      Enum Constants 
      Enum Constant and Description
      COMMITTED

      CONFIRMED

      IN_PROCESS

      NOT_FOUND

      ROLLED_BACK
